Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:14.05,SH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H28DA2E&\4c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(610,142)}2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:14.05,TBA TEAM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(219,404)}TBA Team
