Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.40,0:22:32.07,ed kara,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(420,370)}ochitsukanai nemurenai
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.14,0:22:38.26,ed kara,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}mou nanimo atama ni hairanai
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.33,0:22:45.50,ed kara,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,200)}te wo gutto nobaseba furesou na yubi de
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.50,0:22:52.34,ed kara,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}tada soko mitsumeteru kokoro ga sawaideru
